    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>1. 顺义枫泉花园</name>
      <description><![CDATA[北京顺义出发 · 7:00 走京昆高速 G5 · 约 360km<br/><br/>标签: start<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 116.659905, 40.129109<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=116.659905,40.129109,%E9%A1%BA%E4%B9%89%E6%9E%AB%E6%B3%89%E8%8A%B1%E5%9B%AD&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
