      <Point><coordinates>113.600528,39.008153,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>4. 显通寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[五大禅处之首 · 青铜殿(明万历)+ 铜塔 + 无量殿(国内唯一青铜建筑群) · 必去 0.7<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.596393, 39.009694<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.596393,39.009694,%E6%98%BE%E9%80%9A%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
