      <Point><coordinates>113.596393,39.009694,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>5. 塔院寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[五台山标志性大白塔(高 56.4m · 释迦牟尼舍利塔 · 尼泊尔风格) · 必去 0.6<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.59597, 39.008315<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.59597,39.008315,%E5%A1%94%E9%99%A2%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFF6F00</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.59597,39.008315,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>6. 寿宁寺素斋</name>
      <description><![CDATA[台怀镇寿宁寺素斋 · 17:30 时段 · 11:30 也开 · 错过吃不上<br/><br/>标签: food<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.600029, 39.009154<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.600029,39.009154,%E5%AF%BF%E5%AE%81%E5%AF%BA%E7%B4%A0%E6%96%8B&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
