      <Point><coordinates>113.600029,39.009154,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>7. 五台山宾馆</name>
      <description><![CDATA[台怀镇中心 · 老牌国营 · 21:00 入住 · 旺季提前订<br/><br/>标签: hotel<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.600528, 39.008453<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.600528,39.008453,%E4%BA%94%E5%8F%B0%E5%B1%B1%E5%AE%BE%E9%A6%86&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
