    </Placemark>
  </Folder>
  <Folder>
    <name>D2 佛光寺 + 南禅寺 + 龙泉寺 + 台怀镇核心</name>
    <description>约 100km · 12h · 国保中的国宝 + 加分项</description>
    <Placemark>
      <name>D2 行程连线</name>
      <Style><LineStyle><color>ffE5881E</color><width>3</width></LineStyle></Style>
      <LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>113.394811,38.870102,0 113.120804,38.702103,0 113.578763,39.060999,0 113.600528,39.008453,0 113.599329,39.008854,0 113.600828,39.009454,0 113.601727,39.007652,0 113.601028,39.008453,0 113.600528,39.008453,0</coordinates></LineString>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>1. 佛光寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[国宝中的国宝 · 东大殿(唐 857) · 文殊殿(金 1137) · 祖师塔(北魏) · 必去 1.0 · 1961 第一批国保 · 世界遗产<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.394811, 38.870102<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.394811,38.870102,%E4%BD%9B%E5%85%89%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFF6F00</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.394811,38.870102,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>2. 南禅寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[中国现存最古木构(782 唐建中三年) · 17 尊唐代塑像 · 大佛殿面宽 11.62m · 必去 0.8<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.120804, 38.702103<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.120804,38.702103,%E5%8D%97%E7%A6%85%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
      <Style><IconStyle><color>ffFF6F00</color><scale>1.0</scale><Icon><href>http://maps.google.com/mapfiles/kml/pushpin/ylw-pushpin.png</href></Icon></IconStyle></Style>
      <Point><coordinates>113.120804,38.702103,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>3. 龙泉寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[汉白玉石雕牌坊(山西第一) · 距佛光寺/南禅寺 25km · 加分项 0.3 · 山西省文物保护单位<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.578763, 39.060999<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.578763,39.060999,%E9%BE%99%E6%B3%89%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
