      <Point><coordinates>113.578763,39.060999,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>4. 台怀镇蒙汉餐厅</name>
      <description><![CDATA[返台怀镇午餐 · 12:30 · 手把肉 + 莜面 · 蒙汉兼容<br/><br/>标签: food<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.600528, 39.008453<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.600528,39.008453,%E5%8F%B0%E6%80%80%E9%95%87%E8%92%99%E6%B1%89%E9%A4%90%E5%8E%85&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
