      <Point><coordinates>113.600528,39.008453,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>5. 殊像寺</name>
      <description><![CDATA[文殊菩萨最大铜像(高 9.87m · 5 层楼) · 五台山五大禅处之一 · 加分 0.4<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.599329, 39.008854<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.599329,39.008854,%E6%AE%8A%E5%83%8F%E5%AF%BA&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
