      <Point><coordinates>113.599329,39.008854,0</coordinates></Point>
    </Placemark>
    <Placemark>
      <name>6. 菩萨顶</name>
      <description><![CDATA[康熙乾隆行宫 · 108 级台阶 · 红墙黄瓦 · 五台山五大禅处之一 · 加分 0.3<br/><br/>标签: attract<br/>坐标(GCJ-02): 113.600828, 39.009454<br/>高德导航: <a href="https://uri.amap.com/navigation?to=113.600828,39.009454,%E8%8F%A9%E8%90%A8%E9%A1%B6&mode=car&src=wutaishan">点这里导航</a>]]></description>
